Package io.github.bfox1

Interface IMedusaAPI

  • public interface IMedusaAPI
    The Medusa API Interface gets populated and used by the MedusaBot. The Getters associated with this Interface allow for Plugins to utilize Methods and other function within each Class.

      • createYamlLoader

        IYamlLoader createYamlLoader​(java.lang.String name)
        A Simple Yaml Loader to save and load data. Storing Data in here to keep it persistent when Module or Bot reloads.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        IYamlLoader

      • createConfig

        IConfig createConfig​(java.lang.String moduleName)
        Similar to the createYamlLoader(String) This will create a special config for the Module. Additional information may be stored here. Unlike the IYamlLoader for special use cases, this method has easy access Getters and setters for storing data. If the Config already exists, this method will simply load and return the config already present.
        Parameters:
        moduleName - The name of the Module
        Returns:
        a Config Object.
